The data is taken from chandoo.org . This report consists of:

- Loading and cleaning HR data using Power Query
- Creating HR KPIs such as headcount, average salary, and average leave balance
- Adding calculated columns (employee first name, age group, etc.)
- Analyzing the relationship between salary and education qualification
- Identifying top and bottom paid employees by job role
- Applying filters and slicers for employee-level analysis
- Creating advanced DAX measures such as cumulative headcount and leave balance above 20 days
- Designing an interactive monthly HR dashboard
- Using the new Card visual in Power BI
